And this: Today staff at @MSF's #Ebola treatment center at Butembo began enrolling patients there in the clinical trial of experimental Ebola treatments. So MSF has officially joined the trial.

Two more health workers have been infected with #Ebola. This week's @WHO Disease Outbreak News puts the number now at 67; @WHOAFRO reported 65 earlier this week. (The DON says +5 because it's up 5 from last week.) The most recent death toll I saw was 22.]

